" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有樣野叫形聲字"},{"pid":"48bf6c3746d2917bdb2bee7b060186a782da4692","tid":228733,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英文都衰，拼音唔規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實全世界用德文最好"},{"pid":"241abfefeda11f33f79c3d8e3f4bd28aaa2bee88","tid":228733,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"就算係用拼音，香港人咁多懶音，咪又係串錯曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1742723e360acd98147d513d4773f7cfca945c","tid":228733,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英文都衰，拼音唔規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實全世界用德文最好</blockquote><br />\n英文拼音唔規則，其實係因爲佢地特登要吃力去模仿及貼近拉丁文、法文嘅古老拼法，以圖自我標榜爲羅馬帝國文化繼承正統。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a65cf55462e6943eb094705b9a394154750b776","tid":228733,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算係用拼音，香港人咁多懶音，咪又係串錯曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n調轉諗打得多咪順便糾正埋懶音囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋真係改唔來嘅話 某啲輸入法可以設定「常犯錯誤不敏感」 舉漢語拼音爲例<br />\n<br />\n可能你成日撈亂 &lsquo;z&rsquo; / &lsquo;zh&rsquo; 聲母，咁你可以整到打 &lsquo;z&rsquo; / &lsquo;zh&rsquo; 都出晒兩者開頭所以嘅字<br />\n<br />\n可能有啲1999 sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdeaa33800d50abc526adbaa4cdf1df0affed61","tid":228733,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就算係用拼音，香港人咁多懶音，咪又係串錯曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n調轉諗打得多咪順便糾正埋懶音囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋真係改唔來嘅話 某啲輸入法可以設定「常犯錯誤不敏感」 舉漢語拼音爲例<br />\n<br />\n可能你成日撈亂 &lsquo;z&rsquo; / &lsquo;zh&rsquo; 聲母，咁你可以整到打 &lsquo;z&rsquo; / &lsquo;zh&rsquo; 都出晒兩者開頭<span style=\"color: red;\">所有</span>嘅字<br />\n<br />\n可能有啲1999 sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3bf4c1e2b9d4ac9c3e367c4de1a61ab84f00a85d","tid":228733,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係唔似英文咁 <br />\n可以由讀音trace返隻字點寫<br />\n對我呢d記性差 平時又少寫字 簡直攞命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我勁多簡單字要諗幾分鐘先記得隻字係點樣</span><br />\n利申 頭先想打填充個充字 諗極諗唔到</blockquote><br />\nbtw 紅字：你可能考慮去驗下有無讀寫障礙好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有樣野叫形聲字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係笑／串佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢樣唔係怪病 其實我諗比大衆想像中普遍<br />\n<br />\n講真 如果驗到有 尋求專業協助或者有益 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b466d3998cef4dc465b80e3bdf9f39de05732f3b","tid":228733,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係唔似英文咁 <br />\n可以由讀音trace返隻字點寫<br />\n對我呢d記性差 平時又少寫字 簡直攞命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我勁多簡單字要諗幾分鐘先記得隻字係點樣</span><br />\n利申 頭先想打填充個充字 諗極諗唔到</blockquote><br />\nbtw 紅字：你可能考慮去驗下有無讀寫障礙好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有樣野叫形聲字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係笑／串佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢樣唔係怪病 其實我諗比大衆想像中普遍<br />\n<br />\n講真 如果驗到有 尋求專業協助或者有益 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗應該冇掛<br />\n讀書個陣中文作文成日比老師選做範文<br />\n我記字差對生活影響不大 只係覺得奇怪<br />\n點解幾千隻中文字 明明無跡可尋 都可以記得 還是會唔記得先係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06fc78d22a07b46978ab4eb2c0b375a2cfb2b8e","tid":228733,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就係唔似英文咁 <br />\n可以由讀音trace返隻字點寫<br />\n對我呢d記性差 平時又少寫字 簡直攞命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我勁多簡單字要諗幾分鐘先記得隻字係點樣</span><br />\n利申 頭先想打填充個充字 諗極諗唔到</blockquote><br />\nbtw 紅字：你可能考慮去驗下有無讀寫障礙好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有樣野叫形聲字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係笑／串佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢樣唔係怪病 其實我諗比大衆想像中普遍<br />\n<br />\n講真 如果驗到有 尋求專業協助或者有益 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗應該冇掛<br />\n讀書個陣中文作文成日比老師選做範文<br />\n我記字差對生活影響不大 只係覺得奇怪<br />\n點解幾千隻中文字 明明無跡可尋 都可以記得 還是會唔記得先係正常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係用咗拼音之後個人感覺已經唔再需要記住字形 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7d5cff06f635963efc9ea69e3cb51d155d8f22","tid":228733,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"中文字可以睇字形估意思，英文又得唔得？"},{"pid":"d1b78b4b921056fc2c19ae1707a73f8c7c37227c","tid":228733,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文字可以睇字形估意思，英文又得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n如果你識「字根」，係得"},{"pid":"6d696468497824559eaa55e325ba72d26ca64c2b","tid":228733,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文字可以睇字形估意思，英文又得唔得？</blockquote><br />\nWhy not? <br />\n只不過logographic個morpheme在單字, phoentic在字組"},{"pid":"35a40865353cf3482842083a205fcac16f476947","tid":228733,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英文都衰，拼音唔規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德文會跟！"},{"pid":"0f58dd8cae8806bcd16cdad684951406cfeceb06","tid":228733,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英文都衰，拼音唔規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德文會跟！</blockquote><br />\nFick dich!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4458ddbbe889471c26c2b7209569df793ff5f8c","tid":228733,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"但個好處係你望返幾千年既文都會明<br />\n因為讀音一兩百年演變已經可以好大<br />\n如果文字同讀音掛勾既話, 兩千年前既文一定會嚴重1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f317227608cc2c9619ce338beae10a332cedfe2","tid":228733,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英文都衰，拼音唔規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德文會跟！</blockquote><br />\n根本除左英文絕大多數拼音語言都跟, 英文phonetics根本係弱撚智"},{"pid":"575f6c5b3002ed327546afa19ce731d6bbddbd79","tid":228733,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英文都衰，拼音唔規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德文會跟！</blockquote><br />\nFick dich!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDu Arschloch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cb5ad702edb5ec89c849b025e797add2d208e6","tid":228733,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但個好處係你望返幾千年既文都會明<br />\n因為讀音一兩百年演變已經可以好大<br />\n如果文字同讀音掛勾既話, 兩千年前既文一定會嚴重1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但又可以話呢樣野未必一定好, 全個華語地區唔同語言, 因為漢字呢種特性, 全部都可以統一為一種文字<br />\n容易統一思想, 維持大一統, 兼可以將全部語言屈撚晒做方言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e46ece9620e8bcdde711735ee1c9f5f35701f6","tid":228733,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"應該學日文咁，將漢字變做輔助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓文完全廢漢字，搞到柒哂，反而日文keep得幾好"},{"pid":"02e4302821c9116e49b621a532bb54d40569c3fb","tid":228733,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該學日文咁，將漢字變做輔助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓文完全廢漢字，搞到柒哂，反而日文keep得幾好</blockquote><br />\n應該淨係留返低呀、唔、係、咁、嘅，其他轉做拼音"},{"pid":"c96bf4cb1fa1326188a73296dc49135f3f844a9c","tid":228733,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中文字可以睇字形估意思，英文又得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n如果你識「字根」，係得</blockquote><br />\n讀下理科就知識睇root有幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}